        <article class="text-width">
          <p>I'm Ingo Steinke, a Berlin-based and front-end focused web developer with over 25 years of professional experience. When developing elegant and easy-to-use websites and web apps, I pay attention to accessibility, loading speed and maintainability. HTML, CSS, JavaScript and TypeScript are among my skils as a web developer with a frontend focus. Since 2024, I am a <a href="/services/certified-shopware-developer-berlin.html">certified Shopware developer</a>.
